description:
As part of Fredericksburg Jazz Festival 2020 DIGITAL Randy Brecker talks about his continuing development through a new private teacher and transcribing solos.

To support The Fredericksburg Jazz Festival please donate here: https://fisdband.ludus.com/donate.php

FJF21 (Featuring Randy Brecker) is April 9 & 10, 2021 in Fredericksburg, TX. Buy tickets at: https://fisdband.ludus.com/index.php

*ALL proceeds from Fredericksburg Jazz Festival events benefit the Fredericksburg ISD Jazz program.**
